---
title: Beef Ragù Over Creamy Mashed Potatoes with Peas, Carrots & Crispy Fried Onions
description: In this savory and satisfying dish, ground pork is cooked with sweet carrots and peas, fragrant garlic, and a speedy mirepoix paste for a complex and delicious ragù in no time at all. Piled over buttery mashed potatoes swirled with crème fraîche and sprinkled with crispy golden fried onions, this hearty meal is bursting with flavor. Buon appetito!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65950d69050f2b642e9a27f5-40523cdb.jpeg
